#: xcash/core/models.py:56
msgid "EVM VaultSlot 归集延迟(分钟)"
msgstr "EVM VaultSlot Collection Delay (minutes)"

#: xcash/core/models.py:60
msgid ""
"EVM 到账确认后等待该时间再聚合归集，期间同槽位同币种不重复创建归集计划。EVM "
"默认 60 分钟，兼顾到账归集时效和同槽位批量归集。"
msgstr ""
"After an EVM receipt is confirmed, wait this long before aggregated "
"collection. During this window, duplicate collection schedules are not "
"created for the same slot and currency. The EVM default is 60 minutes, "
"balancing collection timeliness and batching within the same slot."

#: xcash/core/models.py:65
msgid "Tron VaultSlot 归集延迟(分钟)"
msgstr "Tron VaultSlot Collection Delay (minutes)"

#: xcash/core/models.py:69
msgid ""
"Tron 到账确认后等待该时间再聚合归集，期间同槽位同币种不重复创建归集计划。"
"Tron 归集成本高，默认长延迟批量摊薄。"
msgstr ""
"After a Tron receipt is confirmed, wait this long before aggregated "
"collection. During this window, duplicate collection schedules are not "
"created for the same slot and currency. Tron collection is expensive, so the "
"default longer delay amortizes costs through batching."

#: xcash/core/models.py:74
msgid "VaultSlot 最小归集价值(USD)"
msgstr "Minimum VaultSlot Collection Value (USD)"

#: xcash/core/models.py:80
msgid ""
"归集计划到期执行时，槽位该币种余额价值低于该阈值则放弃本次归集（粉尘归集 gas "
"必亏；后续入账使总额达标后会再次调度）。0 表示不限制。"
msgstr ""
"When a collection schedule becomes due, collection is skipped if the slot "
"balance value for that currency is below this threshold (dust collection "
"would lose gas; later deposits that bring the total above the threshold will "
"schedule again). 0 means unlimited."

#: xcash/core/models.py:85
msgid "账单 VaultSlot 单项目单链上限"
msgstr "Per-project Per-chain Invoice VaultSlot Limit"

#: xcash/core/models.py:89
msgid ""
"单个项目在单条链上最多可创建的账单收款 VaultSlot 数量。达到上限后仍可复用已有"
"可用槽位，但不再创建新槽位。"
msgstr ""
"The maximum number of invoice payment VaultSlots a single project can create "
"on one chain. After the limit is reached, existing available slots can still "
"be reused, but no new slots are created."

